# Regression testing

New features must **not break existing behavior**.

## Test inventory

| Area | Automated checks |
| --- | --- |
| **Backend (`backend/`)** | `pytest` |
| **Frontend (`frontend/`)** | `npm run build`, `npm run lint` |

## Verification matrix

| You changed… | Required checks |
| --- | --- |
| **API handler, auth** | `pytest`; extend tests for HTTP-visible behavior |
| **SQL schema** | New Alembic migration only; `pytest` |
| **Error responses** | API tests; confirm frontend parses errors |
| **Vite pages, API client** | `npm run build` + `npm run lint` |

Report which commands you ran when claiming completion.
